PortSystem          1.0

name                diff-pdf
version             0.3
categories          graphics
maintainers         {@pietvo vanoostrum.org:piet}
platforms           darwin
supported_archs     i386 x86_64
license             GPL-2

description         diff-pdf is a tool for visually comparing two PDFs.
long_description \
    It takes two PDF files as arguments. By default, its only output is \
    its return code, which is 0 if there are no differences and 1 if the \
    two PDFs differ. If given the `--output-diff` option, it produces a \
    PDF file with visually highlighted differences. \
    With the `--view` argument it opens a window that lets you view the \
    files' pages and zoom in on details.
       
homepage            http://vslavik.github.io/diff-pdf

PortGroup           github 1.0
github.setup        vslavik diff-pdf 0.3 v
github.tarball_from releases

PortGroup           wxWidgets 1.0
wxWidgets.use       wxWidgets-3.0

checksums           rmd160  938e1f32218a083c2db37e8c220bbde48ef091e7 \
                    sha256  4e91f1094216b98baa22d461b9662b3b6666e49ceb01671e5db6d1a3d384c538 \
                    size    33688

depends_lib         port:poppler \
                    port:cairo \
                    port:wxWidgets-3.0
    
use_autoconf        yes
autoconf.cmd        ./bootstrap

# depends_build must be after use_autoconf due to a quirk
# in trace mode (port -t)

